Augustina Nwaokolo (nke amụrụ na Disemba 12, 1992) bụ onye egwuregwu Naijiria nke na-ebu ibu. O sonyere na ndị asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị 48 kilogram nke 2014 Commonwealth Games ebe o ritere ihe nrite ọla edo.
Augustina Nwaokolo meriri ma rite ọla edo mbụ nke egwuregwu ahụ nke hụrụ ya ka ọ na-etinye ihe ndekọ egwuregwu ọhụrụ nke 175 kilogram mgbe ọ buliechara 77 kilogram na nke akpọrọ snatch na 98 kilogram na nke akpọrọ clean na jerk
Nke a mere ka ọ bụrụ onye Naijiria mbụ na-eto eto na-ebu ibu iji nweta nke ahụ na asọmpi mba ụwa nke akpọrọ Commonwealth Games. E mere ihe omume ahụ na Jawaharlal Nehru Stadium.
